{"tid":809540,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"西九B5超X File","createTime":"2018-09-07T09:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T09:17:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b8108d6c0635c17451434345bb3fa7c747bd88af","tid":809540,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:17:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20180907/20493534\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F20493534&d=y3Nr2Xfmn7RCtyCHc53wQcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=67ebe193\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F20493534&h=9c7e8488\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20180907/20493534</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n西九B5超X File - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180907/large/e8813a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180907%2Flarge%2Fe8813a.jpg&h=98244bfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n消失了的西九B5層，謎一樣，到底有乜用途？有！精選以下幾項：<br />\n<br />\n一，香港要為內地七百（又係柒）執法人員供應每個一百元的飯盒，包四餐，內地大嘥鬼每日生產的廚餘廢物好快以噸計，唔講得笑，好在有B5堆填區。<br />\n<br />\n二，B5神秘莫測，直情可以做片場，政府開鏡，拍一套一地兩檢Lost交叉特區X File。<br />\n<br />\n三，第五層，似有還無，放N隻洗頭艇都無難度。說不定，馬航都擺得落幾隻。B5，勁過百慕達。<br />\n<br />\n四，B5暫時未有規劃，政府又益建制派，將B5劏晒做房，搵埋劏房大使硬銷，經驗老到的劏房波親自打理，應該比年金受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n五，B5有番咁上下，將來唔使去法國，被跌死的紅色商人直接坐高鐵，入閘就得。犯罪家族唔使去油麻地停車場，西九B5等住你們笨豬跳。愛國學者用來殺妻的話，要排隊攞籌。<br />\n<br />\n六，西九冇飯堂，但點可能冇小桃園飯局？B5私房菜日日有局，主菜當然係西環料理，每位689蚊。  <br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n一帶一路一空投？ (尊子)"}]}